ğŸ” Reconnaissance (Baseline Scan)

Ran baseline Nmap scan:

sudo nmap -sS -sV -O -Pn <TARGET> -oA metasploitable_initial


Saved outputs:

metasploitable_initial.nmap â†’ human-readable

